            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media"><img class="img-fluid lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2021-10/oly-2022-beijing-flame-gre-chn-health-virus-092638.jpg?IBk0YUGi9EwW.F3vbfAyZmHj.Wv.ZXnL&itok=iG5DfLuS" title="扮演最高女祭司的希腊女演员乔治乌（Xanthi Georgiou）成功点燃火种。（法新社）" alt="扮演最高女祭司的希腊女演员乔治乌（Xanthi Georgiou）成功点燃火种。（法新社）" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2021-10/oly-2022-beijing-flame-gre-chn-health-virus-092638.jpg?IBk0YUGi9EwW.F3vbfAyZmHj.Wv.ZXnL&itok=iG5DfLuS" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div>
